com.googlecode.flyway.core.api.migration.spring

Interface SpringJdbcMigration


  • public interface SpringJdbcMigration
    Interface to be implemented by Spring Jdbc Java Migrations. By default the migration version and description will be extracted from the class name. This can be overriden by also implementing the MigrationInfoProvider interface, in which case it can be specified programmatically. The checksum of this migration (for validation) will also be null, unless the migration also implements the MigrationChecksumProvider, in which case it can be returned programmatically.
